  "text": "The stability of compound 3 in a physiological-like solution was investigated by NMR and HPLC. Because of the poor water solubility of 3, the complex was previously dissolved in DMSO-d [CITATION_1] and then diluted with deuterated aqueous phosphate buffered saline solution (2 mM, pH 7.4) obtaining a final concentration of 52 µM in DMSO-d 6 /D 2 O (5:95, v/v). The sample was incubated at 37˝C in the dark and 1 H-NMR spectra recorded at different time intervals.",
